		</div>
		<div>
			<div style='min-height:110px;'>In Opencart, customers can upload files but it seems that there is a limit on the file size that they can upload. I would like my customers to be able to upload files up to 100 MB but so far only files of up to 7 MB were able to go through.  I did change the file size limit in Store settings and memory size in php.ini but nothing changed... What else can I do?<br />
